Revision history for NGS-Tools-ANNOVAR

0.01    2014-03-05
        Initial development.  Currently wraps the table_annovar.pl and the
        annotate_variation.pl scripts.

0.02    2014-07-24
        Added ability to pass a target file in BED format to the method
        annotate_variants_with_gene_info_and_variant_databases for custom
        annotations.

0.03    2014-08-03
        Added POD to annotate_variants_wiht_gene_info_and_variant_databases

0.04    2014-08-03
        Cleaned up the code for handling BED files.

0.06    2014-08-25
        Added capability to use VCF as an input and output format.  This works
        with the latest version (as of 2014-08-25) of ANNOVAR.

0.07    2014-11-17
        Updated POD for annotate_variants_with_gene_info_and_variant_databases
        method.  Updated build dependencies.

0.08    2015-07-23
        Added method for handling YAML configuration file to establish
        default values to mandatory arguments.`
